{
  "page": "Lord of the Hornwood",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of the Hornwood</b> is a title<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> held by the rulers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Hornwood_(forest)\" title=\"Hornwood (forest)\">Hornwood</a>, forested land ruled by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Known_Lords_of_the_Hornwood\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Lords of the Hornwood</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Halys_Hornwood\" title=\"Halys Hornwood\">Halys Hornwood</a> and his son and heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Daryn_Hornwood\" title=\"Daryn Hornwood\">Daryn</a>, are killed at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Green_Fork\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of the Green Fork\">Battle of the Green Fork</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Hornwood's widow, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Donella_Hornwood\" title=\"Donella Hornwood\">Donella</a>, becomes Lady of the Hornwood after the deaths of her husband and son. The Hornwood succession is discussed at the <a href=\"/index.php/Harvest_feast\" title=\"Harvest feast\">harvest feast</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a> considers marrying himself or his son <a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Manderly\" title=\"Wendel Manderly\">Wendel</a> to Lady Donella, and claim her lands. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leobald_Tallhart\" title=\"Leobald Tallhart\">Leobald Tallhart</a> proposes that his younger son, <a href=\"/index.php/Beren_Tallhart\" title=\"Beren Tallhart\">Beren</a>, be made Lord of the Hornwood and adopt the Hornwood name, as his wife <a href=\"/index.php/Berena_Hornwood\" title=\"Berena Hornwood\">Berena</a> is the sister of Lord Halys. The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Flint\" title=\"House Flint\">Flints</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">Karstarks</a> are said to have ties to the Hornwood in the female line, as well. Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Brandon Stark</a> considers <a href=\"/index.php/Larence_Snow\" title=\"Larence Snow\">Larence Snow</a> as a possible candidate, the <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> son of the late Lord Hornwood.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a>, the Bastard of <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Bolton</a>, later claims the lands of House Hornwood after forcibly marrying Lady Donella. Ramsay then starves Donella to death in a locked tower.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The now-legitimized Ramsay Bolton styles himself Lord of the Hornwood during his marriage to \"<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>\" (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>) at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_the_Hornwood\">Known Lords of the Hornwood</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of the Hornwood\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Halys_Hornwood\" title=\"Halys Hornwood\">Halys Hornwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Donella_Hornwood\" title=\"Donella Hornwood\">Donella Hornwood</a>, his widow, Lady of the Hornwood after the death of her husband and son</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ramsay Bolton\">Ramsay Bolton</a>, after forcibly marrying Lady Donella</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Reek II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_62\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 62\">Chapter 62</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 35\">Chapter 35</a>, Bran V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 37\">Chapter 37</a>, The Prince of Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404051826\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.022 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 549/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8754/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1982/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 146/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2840/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   13.351      1 -total\n 77.83%   10.391      6 Template:Ref\n 48.24%    6.440      6 Template:Ref/core\n 19.37%    2.586      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:21979-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404051826 and revision id 245355\n -->\n",
